18552 silly resolved     readme: '# is-zip [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/kevva/is-zip.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/kevva/is-zip)\n\n> Check if a Buffer/Uint8Array is a ZIP file\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\n$ npm install --save is-zip\n```\n\n```bash\n$ component install kevva/is-zip\n```\n\n```bash\n$ bower install --save is-zip\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```js\nvar fs = require(\'fs\');\nvar isZip = require(\'is-zip\');\nvar buf = fs.readFileSync(\'foo.zip\');\n\nisZip(buf);\n// => true\n```\n\n## License\n\n[MIT License](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MIT_License) © [Kevin Mårtensson](https://github.com/kevva)\n',
